headline.print_headline: Egypt: Police Arrest Suspect in Rape of Briton
headline.main: Egypt: Police Arrest Suspect in Rape of Briton

lead_paragraph: Egyptian authorities arrested a man on Saturday who is suspected of raping a British citizen in a banana plantation near the ancient southern city of Luxor, a security official said.
